short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Output Keen IO analytics data in the JavaScript console

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Want to make sure the data you're sending to Keen IO is correct? Installing this extension will allow you to view collection name and data for every event sent to Keen IO directly in your dev tools console.
